======
 Poly
======

Installation
============
See instructions in INSTALL.

Scripts
=======
Main scripts:

  polysub  submit job (--help available)
polyxargs  xargs for job arrays

These scripts might be useful:

polylocal  echo filenames that are local copies of the arguments
           if the files are remote
  polyrcp  load-conscious remote copy

These scripts are called by polyjob and you shouldn't ever have to
call them directly

  polyjob  polysub job-wrapping script
 polyxjob  polyxargs job-wrapping script
  polycat  concatenate job output and error files
polywatch  watch job array and ramp up job slot limit
